      passage: `<svg viewBox="0 0 360 250" role="img" aria-label="Line graph of fish counts by month for three species in a Taiwanese tide pool" style="max-width:360px;width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:8px auto"><line x1="52" y1="20" x2="52" y2="210" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="52" y1="210" x2="345" y2="210" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="52" y1="210" x2="345" y2="210" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.18"/><text x="46" y="214" font-size="9" text-anchor="end" fill="currentColor">0</text><line x1="52" y1="149" x2="345" y2="149" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.18"/><text x="46" y="153" font-size="9" text-anchor="end" fill="currentColor">10</text><line x1="52" y1="87" x2="345" y2="87" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.18"/><text x="46" y="91" font-size="9" text-anchor="end" fill="currentColor">20</text><line x1="52" y1="25" x2="345" y2="25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.18"/><text x="46" y="29" font-size="9" text-anchor="end" fill="currentColor">30</text><text x="72" y="224" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor">Jan</text><text x="162" y="224" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor">Apr</text><text x="252" y="224" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor">Jul</text><text x="342" y="224" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor">Oct</text><polyline fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" points="72,204 162,149 252,180 342,180"/><polyline fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="5 3" points="72,210 162,210 252,210 342,192"/><polyline fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-dasharray="2 3" points="72,198 162,204 252,81 342,38"/><polygon points="68,208 76,208 72,200" fill="currentColor"/><polygon points="158,153 166,153 162,145" fill="currentColor"/><polygon points="248,184 256,184 252,176" fill="currentColor"/><polygon points="338,184 346,184 342,176" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="69" y="207" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="159" y="207" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="249" y="207" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="339" y="189" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="72" cy="198" r="3.4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><circle cx="162" cy="204" r="3.4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><circle cx="252" cy="81" r="3.4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><circle cx="342" cy="38" r="3.4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><text x="200" y="13" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="600" fill="currentColor">Fish observed in a Taiwanese Tide Pool, 2001</text><text x="10" y="115" font-size="8.5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-90 10 115)">Number of individual fish</text><text x="360" y="115" font-size="8" text-anchor="end" fill="currentColor">▲ frillgoby &nbsp;■ blenny &nbsp;○ sergeant</text></svg><div style="margin-top:6px">Lin-Tai Ho and colleagues monitored fish populations in a tide pool in Taiwan. They found that some species were entirely absent from the tide pool at particular times of the year; for example, they did not observe even one ______</div>`,
      prompt: `Which choice most effectively uses data from the graph to complete the example?`,
      options: [{ id: `A`, text: `wavy-lined blenny in January, April, and July of 2001` }, { id: `B`, text: `Indo-Pacific sergeant in October of 2001` }, { id: `C`, text: `Indo-Pacific sergeant in July of 2001` }, { id: `D`, text: `Cocos frillgoby in April of 2001` }],
